 egin by acknowledging the land&#8217\;s original indigenous stewards\, the
 n discuss Native American history\, culture\, and practices as we hike thi
 s beautiful trail. Hike leader Amy Ransford is a historian whose research 
 centers on Native and European peoples in the colonial Hudson River Waters
 hed.
